preRequisites: Counter shift should be started for User
title: Normal Registration
text: Verify Normal registration
steps:
1.Launch the application
2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select Registration from the drop down.
4.Select Type of registration as “Normal”
5.Enter  the  Mandatory Details which are having asterisk(*)symbol and click on the “Register” button.
6.Enter Payment details by selecting payment mode as CARD/CASH etc
7.Click on submit button
expectedResults: Valid UHID should get generate with details and should be able to take the print of that receipt

title: Update details
text: Verify "Update details" feature by updating existing Patient details
steps:
1.Launch the application
2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select Registration from the drop down.
4.Click on patient search link
5.Enter valid UHID or patient details like first name ,last name and gender for search and click on search button
6.Right click on UHID click on Update details and do some changes like change title or marital status.
7.Click on Update record.
expectedResults: Details should get update Successfully

title: Conversion from PRN/ERN Reg to UHID
text: Verify Conversion from PRN/ERN Reg to UHID
steps:
1.Launch the application
2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select Registration from the drop down.
4.Click on patient search link
5.Enter input values like PRN/ERN and click on search button
6.Right click on PRN/ERN and click on convert to UHID link 
7.Enter mandatory Details which are having asterisk(*)symbol and click on convert to UHID button
8.Enter Payment details by selecting payment mode as CARD/CASH etc
9.Click on submit button
expectedResults: Should get convert successfully from PRN/ERN Reg to UHID

title: UHID with Cash Payment
text: Verify To generate UHID with Cash Payment
steps:
1.Launch the application
2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select Registration from the drop down.
4.Select Type of registration as “Normal”                                                               5.Check Yes for International patients and enter the mandatory  fields.
6.Enter  the  Mandatory Details which are having asterisk(*) symbol and click on the “Register” button.
7.Check the transaction billable check box and check the “Cash”  payment mode in Payment details. (By default the transaction check box is checked).
8. Select the Currency and give currency amount in Cash details(Total cash amount should be equivalent to the billable amount)
expectedResults: UHID should get generate with cash Payment

title: UHID with Card Payment

steps:

2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select Registration from the drop down.
4.Select Type of registration as “Normal”                                                               5.Check Yes for International patients and enter the mandatory  fields.
6.Enter  the  Mandatory Details which are having asterisk(*) symbol and click on the “Register” button.
7.Check the transaction billable check box and check the “Card”  payment mode in Payment details. (By default the transaction check box is checked) provide the required details and do payment.
expectedResults: UHID should get generate with card Payment

3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select AT from the drop down.
4.Select Bed booking from Functions drop down.
5.Enter the valid UHID number.
6.Select Type of Booking 
7.Select Admission Note Type as Paper.
8.Select Specializations and Doctor Name
9.Select MLC, Isolation Required, Infectious Check Boxes if required.
10. Upload and Document if needed,and add comments.
11. Select First Choice and Second Choice 
12.Select Expected Admission Date and time and Reason For Booking, Attendent Name, Phone Number, Relationship and Address.
13.Click on save button.
expectedResults: User should be able to create a Bed Booking using Paper Transaction

title: Bed Booking - Bed Booking - Online
text: To Verify the user able to create new Bed Booking
steps:
1.Launch the application
2.Login to the application with valid credentials.
3.Click on Patient Service Tab and select AT from the drop down.
4.Select Bed booking from Functions drop down.
5.Enter the valid UHID number.
6.Select Type of Booking 
7.Select Admission Note Type as Online.
8.Admisssion Number will be generated.
9.Select First Choice and Select Second Choice option from Dro Down.
10.Select Expected Date and Time and Reason fot Booking.
11. Attendent Name, Phone Number, Relationship and Address.
12.Click on save button.
expectedResults: User should be able to create a Bed Booking using Online Transaction
